Package: croplandbias
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of error in landcover datasets using SA reference data
Description: This package contains the the data, analyses, and manuscript source
  for the Estes et al (2017), "A Large-Area, Spatially Continuous Assessment of 
  Land Cover Map Error and Its Impact on Downstream Analyses", in Global Change
  Biology
Version: 0.5.9
Date: "`r Sys.Date()`"
Author: Lyndon Estes <LEstes@clarku.edu>
Maintainer: Lyndon Estes <LEstes@clarku.edu>
Depends:
    TeachingDemos,
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    lmisc,
    raster,
    rgdal,
    dtraster
Imports:
    lmisc,
    raster,
    rgdal,
    dtraster
License: GPL (>= 3)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
LazyData: TRUE
